2026-05-15T06:28:15.5827648Z 224            Harden Google Play Billing's proxy activities so the system
2026-05-15T06:28:15.5828472Z 225            cannot restore them from Recents or after process death with a
2026-05-15T06:28:15.5829288Z 226            stale Intent. The library's onCreate reads the PendingIntent
2026-05-15T06:28:15.5830091Z 227            extra without null-checking; if Android recreates the activity
2026-05-15T06:28:15.5830781Z 228            and the extra is missing, it NPEs on
2026-05-15T06:28:15.5831496Z 229            PendingIntent.getIntentSender(). noHistory + excludeFromRecents
2026-05-15T06:28:15.5832351Z 230            finishes the activity as soon as it leaves the foreground so it
2026-05-15T06:28:15.5833129Z 231            is never re-entered with a missing extra. Library 8.x adds its
2026-05-15T06:28:15.5833856Z 232            own configChanges absorber and a v2 proxy, both of which we
2026-05-15T06:28:15.5834495Z 233            preserve via tools:node="merge".
